dom on countless biology majors and was instrumental in placing many of them into medical school and dental school  The fund has grown significantly over the years  providing money for equipment purchases and affording the department the opportunity to monetarily reward cadets for outstanding academic performance  Contributions to the Carroll Fund can be made through the VMI Foundation  VMI Foundation Keydet Club Alumni Webcams Directories My VMI  RESOURCES   Title IX  Health   Safety   IT   Site Index Parents   Families   Cadets   Non discrimination Statement   Privacy   THE VMI PHILOSOPHY The VMI experience is framed by relevant education within a military environment  It s an education that develops character  fosters a lifelong appreciation of physical fitness engenders a sense of responsibility to others  and cultivates the ability to master adversity  VIRGINIA MILITARY INSTITUTE Lexington  Virginia 24450 General Information   540  464 7230  Admissions  admissions vmi edu 